title: IT WAS THE BEST!!!
review: I loved it, i would pay to see it ten times, (or more) it was the best!!! if anybody who goes and sees it, doesnt like it, they must be crazy!it is, in my opinion better than titanic. LEO KICKS THAT MOVIES BUTT! TOM HANKS WAS EXCELENT TOO. i also liked christopher walken...what am i saying? the whole cast was great....GO SEE IT! YOU'LL LOVE IT!
